reviewText: Great resource for a children's ministry.  Kids love the songs, and it's great to have video to go along with them!  Great product!

My children love it! We use it in children's church and the kids love it!
Great fun songs all can enjoy!
Our children's ministry really loves this collection.  Great graphics and words to every song. I would suggest this for 3-6th graders and the younger ones enjoy it right along with our big kids!
The songs were a little outdated, but the last 2 songs are so much fun! Really loved I am a C! I wish there was more adult singing and not as much children's singing.
